objects.name: cheeky chipmunk
objects.description: Cheeky Chipmunk is a malicious Microsoft Windows Remote Procedure Call (RPC) server installed via a PowerShell loader. It is tasked by a separate RPC client and can execute shell commands, upload, and download files.

objects.name: Cheeky Chipmunk_command_argument_check
objects.description: YARA rule to detect related activity.
objects.pattern: rule CheekyChipmunk_command_argument_check { meta: author = "NCSC" description = "Detects Cheeky Chipmunk argument checking code to determine command to process. " date = "2022-01-24" hash1 = "7e4a6bac09ad214e98801bc199f96c265d7b6b48" strings: $1 = {66 83 F8 70 75 ?? C7 85 ?? FD FF FF 01 00 00 00 EB ??} $2 = {66 83 F8 63 75 ?? C7 85 ?? FD FF FF 03 00 00 00 EB ??} $3 = {66 83 F8 67 75 ?? C7 85 ?? FD FF FF 02 00 00 00 EB ??} $4 = {66 83 F8 72 75 ?? C7 85 ?? FD FF FF 01 00 00 00 EB ??} condition: uint16(0) == 0x5A4D and uint32(uint32(0x3c)) == 0x00004550 and all of them }

objects.name: CheekyChipmunk_GUID_bytes
objects.description: YARA rule to detect related activity.
objects.pattern: rule CheekyChipmunk_GUID_bytes { meta: author = "NCSC" description = "Detects the Cheeky Chipmunk RPC GUID" date = "2022-01-24" hash1 = "52c8cbd0545caab7596c1382c7fc5a479209851d" hash2 = "865f4c457bf86ff03456de828044f6ed6d6cf96a" hash3 = "5d5825b14377c5e5fe96816dd72a90bd13dc9fc8" hash4 = "7e4a6bac09ad214e98801bc199f96c265d7b6b48" strings: $GUID = {64 25 F0 7D 1E C3 68 4A A6 88 72 D0 EC 84 07 46} condition: uint16(0) == 0x5A4D and uint32(uint32(0x3c)) == 0x00004550 and all of them }

objects.name: Create or Modify System Process: Windows Service
objects.description: Cheeky Chipmunk maintains persistence by adding a new Windows service (pnrssp) for the RPC server component.

objects.name: Command and Scripting Interpreter: PowerShell
objects.description: Open-source PowerShell runner code is embedded in the Cheeky Chipmunk RPC server and used to invoke commands stored in the registry.

objects.name: Command and Scripting Interpreter: Windows Command Shell
objects.description: The Cheeky Chipmunk RPC server can be sent Windows shell commands by the RPC client.

objects.name: Inter-Process Communication: Component Object Model
objects.description: The Cheeky Chipmunk RPC server uses COM to call embedded PowerShell runner code.

objects.name: Deobfuscate/Decode Files or Information
objects.description: The Cheeky Chipmunk loader uses built-in and open-source PowerShell libraries to Base64-decode, 3DES-decrypt, and GZIP-decompress the RPC server.

objects.name: Indicator Removal on Host: File Deletion
objects.description: The Cheeky Chipmunk loader is deleted from disk once the RPC server is running.

objects.name: Masquerading: Match Legitimate Name or Location
objects.description: Cheeky Chipmunk masquerades as a legitimate Windows service path (netsvcs) to maintain persistence.

objects.name: Obfuscated Files or Information
objects.description: Cheeky Chipmunk's import names are obfuscated by XORing with 0x55.

objects.name: Impair Defenses: Disable or Modify Tools
objects.description: Cheeky Chipmunk implements an AMSI bypass technique.

objects.name: Data from Local System
objects.description: Cheeky Chipmunk can be tasked to collect files.

objects.name: Analisi Malware: Cheeky Chipmunk
objects.description: This report contains technical analysis and indicators associated with malware. cheeky chipmunk.
